{"tid":1177980,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《Sing Street / 初戀無限JAM》","createTime":"2019-05-30T06:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T17:38:14.000Z","uid":76885,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c54489642dd848390ec075fd27310452e14a2fd7","tid":1177980,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:16:55.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n//<em>先問你一個處境問題。中學雞年代，一個風和日麗的早上，你遇到一個很cool，但是很索的女孩。你腦海中立刻浮現出三個選擇。<br />\n選擇A：輕嘆一句這些機會不是屬於我的，然後轉身離開；<br />\n選擇B：找個機會壁咚她，然後抄牌；<br />\n選擇C：吹噓自己是樂團主音，並邀請女孩做MV女主角。<br />\n<br />\n你會如何選擇？<br />\n<br />\n「咁破格，咁都得？」或許你心中不禁驚訝。不過，《初戀無限Jam》裏面的男主角Conor 正正採用了選擇C的方法。很荒誕，但也很勇敢。或許無論是把妹，還是追夢，要成功就是需要那種一無所懼的衝動吧？<br />\n<br />\n美少女Raphina 爽快答應了偽Band友的邀請。而為了弄假成真，Conor 只好四處拉人，硬著頭皮去組建一隊樂隊。於是一個把毒撚變成真 &middot; Band友的熱血故事就在1985年的都柏林展開了。</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/personal/%E5%88%9D%E6%88%80%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90jam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%2588%2580%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2599%2590jam%2F&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuickcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=fdfba0bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%2588%2580%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2599%2590jam%2F&h=1f59f37b\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/personal/%E5%88%9D%E6%88%80%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90jam/</a><br />\n<br />\n2<br />\nSing Street (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack)<br />\n1 Rock N Roll Is a Risk&quot; (Dialogue) - Jack Reynor<br />\n2 Stay Clean - 摩托頭<br />\n3 The Riddle of Model - Sing Street<br />\n4 Rio - 杜蘭杜蘭<br />\n5 Up - Sing Street<br />\n6 To Find You - Sing Street<br />\n7 Town Called Malice - The Jam<br />\n8 In Between Days - 治療樂隊<br />\n9 A Beautiful Sea - Sing Street<br />\n10 Maneater - 賀爾與奧茲<br />\n11 Steppin' Out - 喬&middot;積遜<br />\n12 Drive It Like You Stole It - Sing Street<br />\n13 Up (Bedroom Mix) - Sing Street<br />\n14 Pop Muzik - M樂隊<br />\n15 Girls - Sing Street<br />\n16 Brown Shoes - Sing Street<br />\n17 Go Now - 亞當&middot;李維<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xko3ZGt7wSc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fxko3ZGt7wSc&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuickcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=042fb7c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xko3ZGt7wSc</a><br />\n<br />\n3<br />\n有無人有睇過呢套？<br />\n啱啱睇完，覺好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f078114ba1f5ed878b0a01a62c1b6b6914440cff","tid":1177980,"uid":76885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:19:26.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cinezen.hk/?p=6672\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cinezen.hk%2F%3Fp%3D6672&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuickcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=a0765ff6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cinezen.hk/?p=6672</a><br />\n<br />\n//<em>犬儒的退縮，卻在飾演哥哥Brendan的Jack Reynor中最表露無遺。面對父母爭吵不斷，生活備受壓抑，現實的挫折，出走失敗的經歷，彷彿已了解世界的全部黑暗和變成永遠的失敗者，「看透世情」般不屑與世界同流合污。事實是Brendan依舊若無其事地追逐當下的潮流，對家人侃侃而談，卻從未真正踏出家庭這個「舒適區」（comfort zone）嘗試實踐自己的理想，到頭來一切恐懼與困難全在他自築於內心的磚牆。<br />\n<br />\n哲學家齊澤克（Slavoj Žižek） 如此看待「犬儒」：「他們知道，他們實際上只是在跟循一種虛幻，但仍然，他們正在這樣做」，而犬儒本身導致大眾公共生活的退卻，正因為對現實的無力感與逃避處理真正面對的各種問題，不也恰恰是Brendan的寫照嗎？既無力反抗，倒不如放棄自己，否定外面的世界，連父母離異分居，他也只想迴避這眼前的問題：反正事實如此，索性「鬥HEA」。</em><br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n幾鍾意個啊哥既角色。<br />\n<br />\n3<br />\n//<em>男女主角航向希冀中的新天新地，正好是踐行「Rock n&rsquo;Roll is a risk」的理想，若每個人願意在日常中踏出自己的框框，改變的將會不啻是個人，而是社會。</em>"},{"pid":"d4501a19b61244cc9e8b8a48bfbf3b1158a0b6ed","tid":1177980,"uid":2811,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:21:32.000Z","msg":"呢套幾正不過對比Once同Begin Again好似少好多人討論<br />\n哥哥個角色同舞會段戲都拍得好<br />\nTo Find You &amp; Drive It Like You Stole It<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a39940eb11e80519688a780778e0275dd656e56","tid":1177980,"uid":161780,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"我勁鍾意呢套戲！睇完好有feel<br />\n歌又好聽"},{"pid":"c39f3134bf2ec0744615f596027cf257c210f140","tid":1177980,"uid":33772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"睇完成套戲加埋結局嗰幕 覺得個心靈洗滌左咁<br />\n啲音樂好正 當年睇完即刻去買埋隻soundtrack"},{"pid":"72970d8991f1eeb238056f68cfb6a0520d699150","tid":1177980,"uid":76885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c39f3134bf2ec0744615f596027cf257c210f140","tid":1177980,"uid":33772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"睇完成套戲加埋結局嗰幕 覺得個心靈洗滌左咁<br />\n啲音樂好正 當年睇完即刻去買埋隻soundtrack"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"結局太美好，我對個結尾少d感覺。<br />\n反而好俾主角既行動力，同過程中既順利所表現既運氣所感染 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1<br />\n為愛情為性欲？而去說謊。<br />\n然後以謊言為起點，去行動，然後將謊言成為現實。<br />\n<br />\n主角一路行動，世界就好似一路順利咁幫佢，安排佢遇到最適合既野：<br />\n無論係死物既工具、他人，或靈感。<br />\n<br />\n然後，慢慢謊言，被實現到一部分，變成現實後，謊言就永遠唔會再係謊言，倒頭睇，反而係一種宣言。<br />\n<br />\n當主角遇惡霸，因自己有能力創作而有自信，唔再怕惡霸只識破壞既暴力：<br />\n呢點我好感動？唔知可唔可以叫感動，但總之好有feel：<br />\n要贏人，甚至係要贏暴力既人，唔一定要同對方喺同一個領域，譬如變得好打先可以打贏對方：<br />\n只要有d aspect有實力，然後有自信，就可以由對方既心開始擊潰對方。<br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n睇到呢d位，有諗：<br />\n我自己呢？<br />\n有咩想實現？<br />\n有咩夢想，或創作，想做？<br />\n<br />\n有咩可以立即行動？<br />\n<br />\n3<br />\n未知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b028551172d30a3b26f7e3aef3f7dc2b383464","tid":1177980,"uid":33772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇睇埋John Carney另外兩套 Once同Begin Again? 雖然我都係覺得Sing Street正啲<br />\n另外推薦God help the girl"},{"pid":"aa0c4e7b4d1746ca98b9a3c37276b20a4ac2fb41","tid":1177980,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78b028551172d30a3b26f7e3aef3f7dc2b383464","tid":1177980,"uid":33772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇睇埋John Carney另外兩套 Once同Begin Again? 雖然我都係覺得Sing Street正啲<br />\n另外推薦God help the girl"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:13:40.000Z","msg":"無睇前二 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話我睇左最正，咁暫時唔花時間睇前二 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGod嗰套，search下先，謝介紹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d663e7a03b73018800eed784543f1c35d951a5e","tid":1177980,"uid":76885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dopvhmj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdopvhmj.jpg&h=f5a63cc1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nCover已覺吸引 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d32582401d349db05068b41d5fe3764c5e3beec","tid":1177980,"uid":122060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78b028551172d30a3b26f7e3aef3f7dc2b383464","tid":1177980,"uid":33772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇睇埋John Carney另外兩套 Once同Begin Again? 雖然我都係覺得Sing Street正啲<br />\n另外推薦God help the girl"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:24:34.000Z","msg":"Belle and sabestian !!! 識野"},{"pid":"4d7cc1e0d12b895d8fa4d2e1c71519cac301de97","tid":1177980,"uid":6800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"比起once同Begin again 我更加鐘意sing street <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲歌勁正<br />\n個故事好過癮<br />\n<br />\nGod help the girl啲歌又係好好j<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf268f25ea6690206d320fbd146f343de8d57bd","tid":1177980,"uid":204531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"呢套係我top 10之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戲院睇左三次 結局配埋首歌好撚熱血 導演三套我都好鍾意 <br />\n估唔到女主角而家爆左出黎 Ermond又去左拍youtube劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk